    <p>
      We offer practical and furnished accommodation for workers and companies
      temporarily working in Sweden.
    </p>

    <p>
      The focus is on functionality, simplicity and a reliable place to stay
      during the work period.
    </p>
  </Fragment>

  <section>
    <img
      class="example-image"
      src="https://picsum.photos/900/400?random=1"
      alt="Exempelbild av boende"
    />
