    <p>
      Our accommodations are designed for everyday living and are suitable
      for both individuals and work teams.
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li>Bed and storage</li>
      <li>Kitchen with basic equipment</li>
      <li>Bathroom with shower</li>
      <li>Internet</li>
      <li>Laundry facilities</li>
    </ul>

